asadaki Kuran çevirilerinin zamanla daha iyilerinin yapılacağına inanıyoruz. Ayrıca bu konuda, Kuran ayetlerini konularına göre ayıran kitaplardan da yararlanabilirsiniz. İnsan yorumları, gelenekler, uydurmalar atılınca ve Kuran tek kaynak kabul edilince gerçek din ortaya çıkacaktır.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-d_W4eFT0G_U\/VFE125s3WII\/AAAAAAAAAS8\/y_SgGWvkfT8\/s1600\/38.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cimg border=\"0\" src=\"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-d_W4eFT0G_U\/VFE125s3WII\/AAAAAAAAAS8\/y_SgGWvkfT8\/s1600\/38.jpg\" \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cb\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: red; font-size: large;\"\u003EBUNLAR KURAN’DA = DİN’DE VAR\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/b\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003EAllah’ın varlığı ve birliği\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003EAllah’a eşler koşmadan iman etmek\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003EAllah’ın merhameti, cömertliği ve affediciliği\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003EAllah’ı hem sevmek, hem de Allah’tan korkmak\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003EAllah’ın her şeyin yaratıcı