r. Yani geleneklerden hareketle, “Böyle gördük, biz de böyle yapıyoruz” mantığıyla\u0026nbsp;yapılan uygulamalar, kelle sayımı ile gerçeği bulmalar Kuran’ın anlattığı İslam ile bağdaşmaz. Kuran’a göre, Kuran’ın kendisi “beyyine”dir (açık delildir). Bu yüzden ancak Kuran’ı dinin tek kaynağı yapanlar açık delile uymuş olurlar.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"background-color: white; line-height: 19.2000007629395px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"color: #525252; line-height: 1.9em;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"line-height: 1.9em;\"\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\"tr_bq\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: purple; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EB\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eu\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003En\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ela\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Erı Kuran’da türlü türlü şekillerde (sarf) açıkladık ki öğüt alıp hatırlasınlar. Fakat bu sadece kaçışlarını artırıyor.\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/blockquote\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"color: #525252; line-height: 1.9em;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E17-İsra Suresi 41\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"color: #525252; line-height: 1.9em;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\"line-height: 1.9em;\"\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\"tr_bq\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: purple; font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EA\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003End\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eo\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003El\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Es\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eu\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003En bu Kuran’da her örnekten insanlar için