ikle suçlamaya gelince alaya almıyorsun, iki laf atınca hemen alevleniyorsun, noldu dostum\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv dir=\"ltr\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cb style=\"color: blue;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E- Barış Seven:\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/b\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u0026nbsp;Kâfirûn, 2.. Ayet: \"Ben, sizin taptıklarınıza tapmam.\"\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKâfirûn, 3.. Ayet: \"Siz de benim taptığıma tapmazsınız.\"\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKâfirûn, 4.. Ayet: \"Ben asla sizin taptığınıza tapacak değilim.\"\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKâfirûn, 5.. Ayet: \"Siz de benim taptığıma tapacak değilsiniz.\"\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EKâfirûn, 6.. Ayet: \"Sizin dininiz size, benim dinim bana.\"\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv dir=\"ltr\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit;\"\u003E\u003Cb style=\"color: blue;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E- Barış Seven:\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/b\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: blue;\"\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/span\u003EAlevlendim mi sanıyorsun ;)\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv dir=\"ltr\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: large;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: red;\"\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cb style=\"color: red;\"\u003E- Eş Tutan:\u003C\/b\u003E\u0026nbsp;Kendini nebi sanan akılsıza selam olsun\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u0